Jack Denton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Denton 0 Jack Denton (11 September 1872 – 19 April 1949) was a British actor and film director of the silent era.Denton was born as John Fleming St. Andrew Denton in Ashby-de-la-Zouch, Leicestershire, He died at age 76 in Redhill, Surrey.
